@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK
@EndUserText.label: 'Vehicle Inward Header BO View'
define root view entity ZWBI_I_VEHIN_HEAD
  as select from zwbi_vinh as _Head //zdt_vehin_head as _Head  
  composition [0..*] of ZWBI_I_VEHIN_ITEM as _Item // ZI_VEHIN_ITEM as _Item
  association [0..1] to I_Plant as _Planttext on $projection.Plant = _Planttext.Plant  //01-04 */
 

{
  key inward_uuid           as Inward_Uuid, 
      ticknum               as Ticknum,
      fiscal                as Fiscal,
      intype                as Intype,
      indate                as Indate,
      intime                as Intime,
      vehnum                as Vehnum, 
      drivname              as Drivname,
      drivnum               as Drivnum, 
      tranname              as Tranname,
      orderhead             as Orderhead,  
      plant                 as Plant,
      planttext             as Planttext,
      type                  as Type,
      dchannel              as Dchannel,
      range                 as Range,
      printform             as Printform,
      pwidate               as Pwidate,
      pwiempwg              as Pwiempwg,
      pwigetwg              as Pwigetwg,
      pwitime               as Pwitime,
      pwiuom                as Pwiuom,
      pwodate               as Pwodate,             
      pwotime               as Pwotime,
      itemunit              as Itemunit, 
      grossweight           as Grossweight,
      netweight             as Netweight,
      pwoempwg              as Pwoempwg,  //29-05
      pwogetwg              as Pwogetwg,
      pwexit                as Pwexit,
      pwexitdt              as Pwexitdt,
      pwexittm              as Pwexittm,   
      hdevlstatus           as Hdevlstatus,  //09-04 
      shippoint             as shippoint,
      shipptext             as shipptext,
      pwoempwg_f            as Pwoempwg_f,           
      pwiempwg_f            as Pwiempwg_f,            
      gunit_f               as Gunit_f,                   
      tunit_f               as Tunit_f,    
      itemunit_f            as Itemunit_f,  //25/10/2024
      grossweight_f         as Grossweight_f,       
      netweight_f           as Netweight_f,     
      pwiuom_f              as Pwiuom_f,  
//      @Semantics.user.createdBy: true
      created_by            as CreatedBy,
      @Semantics.systemDateTime.createdAt: true
      created_at            as CreatedAt,
      created_tm            as CreatedTm,
      @Semantics.dateTime: true
      created_on            as CreatedOn,
      last_changed_by       as LastChangedBy,
      last_changed_on       as LastChangedOn,
      @Semantics.systemDateTime.lastChangedAt: true
      last_changed_at       as LastChangedAt,
      @Semantics.systemDateTime.localInstanceLastChangedAt: true
      local_last_changed_at as LocalLastChangedAt,
      eflag                 as Eflag,
      last_changed_by_n    as Last_changed_by_n,
      _Item,
      _Planttext 
 
}
